About the Project
My Project, Fluctuation between 3 Cities, is about trying to compared the housing price fluctuation of three major city in US, how each city performs and trying to find why this is the case"
Goals
Graph 3 lines of date vs HPI
Fill with colors
Interactive
Making the points move or have motion
